 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EAmerican Securities is a leading middle-market private equity firm with one of the most consistent track records in the industry of building successful, enduring businesses.  We invest in companies with revenues ranging from $100 million to $1 billion. Currently investing our $2.3 billion fifth fund with an unprecedented 25-year time horizon, our strategy is to:\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EInvest in market-leading companies in stable demand industries\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECreate distinctive relationships with all of our business partners: sellers, CEOs, management teams, banks and investors.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EEmploy a conservative capital structure with no subordinated debt.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EWork diligently with management teams to be a value-added partner. Our Resources Group includes world-class functional experts who are full-time American Securities\u00e2\u20ac\u2122 employees available to portfolio company management teams on request.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThrough this approach, we generate and preserve wealth for our investors and for our management teams for the long-term. \u003C/p\u003E",
